    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a masterpiece of automotive history that feels less like a machine and more like a whispered promise of the open road. This pristine silhouette doesn't just travel; it arrives. The deep, glass-like finish of the paint reflects the world around it with breathtaking clarity, while the interior envelops you in the rich, intoxicating aroma of hand-stitched leather and polished timber. Every switch clicks with the deliberate precision of a Swiss watch, and the engine\u2019s purr is a low, rhythmic heartbeat that suggests endless possibilities. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved with a level of devotion usually reserved for fine art\u2014a true survivor that looks and feels as though it has been frozen in its most glorious moment.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
