    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It\u2019s not every day I get to part with a gem like this, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride of their life. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one\u2014it\u2019s been tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and has honestly never seen a rainy day. The condition is just spectacular; it looks and smells like it just left the showroom. Whether you\u2019re a collector or just want the best of the best, you won\u2019t find another one this clean. Come on over, let's talk shop, and I'll show you why this is the one you've been waiting for!",
      "price": 48900.0,
