    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered here is an absolute pinnacle-spec E92 M3, featuring the iconic S65 V8 with a bespoke maintenance pedigree. This unit has undergone a comprehensive preventative overhaul, including VAC coated rod bearings and ARP rod bolts to solidify the bottom end for another 100k miles. The M-DCT gearbox features a GTS software recalibration, optimizing shift points and clamping pressure. The suspension geometry is laser-aligned, and the subframe mounting points have been proactively reinforced to handle the high-G loads this chassis was designed for. Zero thermal degradation on the cooling system and a pristine interior cockpit. This is a turn-key, apex-ready machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
